OL,3,CPolice called to council meeting after
OL,4,Cexplosive argument in chamber
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports political
OL,7,Fcorrespondent Lise McNally takes a
OL,8,Flook at the explosive night in the
OL,9,Fchamber
OL,11,FPolice officers had to be called to a
OL,12,Fcouncil meeting after an "explosive"
OL,13,Fargument between councillors led to
OL,14,Fclaims of a political group leader and
OL,15,Fhis deputy squaring up to each other.
OL,17,FIt is claimed Nazi insults were used
OL,18,Fas councillors began hurling abuse at
OL,19,Feach other during the Oldham Council
OL,20,Fmeeting.
