OL,3,CPolice called to council meeting after
OL,4,Cexplosive argument in chamber
OL,6,FIndependent Councillor Marc Hince
OL,7,Fclaims he was called a Nazi "without
OL,8,Fany reason or provocation" during the
OL,9,Fdebate around withdrawing from the
OL,10,F'Places for Everyone' scheme, a long-
OL,11,Fterm plan of nine Greater Manchester
OL,12,Fdistricts to create jobs, new homes,
OL,13,Fand sustainable growth.
OL,15,FIn a statement he said: "During last
OL,16,Fnight's full council meeting... two
OL,17,FConservative members called me a Nazi,
OL,18,Fwithout any reason or provocation.
OL,19,FSomething I find deeply offensive and
OL,20,Fabsolutely uncalled for.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
