OL,3,CPolice called to council meeting after
OL,4,Cexplosive argument in chamber
OL,6,F"Naturally, I challenged the
OL,7,Findividual vociferously. However, I
OL,8,Freflected on my actions and apologised
OL,9,Funreservedly to all elected members
OL,10,Fand the chamber as a whole.
OL,12,F"Unfortunately, despite requests from
OL,13,Fthe mayor and their own Group Leader
OL,14,Fthey refused to apologise."
OL,16,FIt is believed during the break an
OL,17,Fargument arose between the deputy of
OL,18,Fthe Oldham Conservatives Lewis Quigg
OL,19,Fand the Conservative leader Graham
OL,20,FSheldon.
