OL,3,CPolice called to council meeting after
OL,4,Cexplosive argument in chamber
OL,6,FConservative Group Leader Graham
OL,7,FSheldon said the meeting
OL,8,F"disintegrated into shambles" after
OL,9,Ftwo of the party's members "caused the
OL,10,Fmeeting to deteriorate as it did".
OL,12,F"If you've made a mistake, said
OL,13,Fsomething out of order, you man up,
OL,14,Fapologise," he said.
OL,16,F"It's quite simple to do, they had the
OL,17,Fopportunity twice. It disintegrated
OL,18,Finto a shambles. It does nothing for
OL,19,Fthe town of Oldham and the council and
OL,20,Fthe residents."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
