OL,7,F"It put Oldham in a poor light.
OL,9,F"The majority of Oldham people don't
OL,10,Fexpect that behaviour within Council.
OL,12,F"We shouldn't get aggressive and we
OL,13,Fshouldn't be personal to any member of
OL,14,Fthe public or officers alike."
