OL,4,Cexplosive argument in chamber
OL,6,FFollowing the meeting leader of the
OL,7,Fcouncil, Arooj Shah, slammed the
OL,8,F"disrespectful" councillors and said
OL,9,Fshe would be bringing together
OL,10,FOldham's political group leaders to
OL,11,Freignite a "politics not
OL,12,Fpersonalities" campaign, which started
OL,13,Fin 2021 to combat some of the 'toxic
OL,14,Fidentity politics' that was plaguing
OL,15,FOldham's chambers.
OL,17,FDescribing the scenes as a "step too
OL,18,Ffar", she said: "I will stress this is
OL,19,Fa handful of members - most members
OL,20,Ffrom all parties and groups treat the
OL,21,Fchamber with the respect it deserves.
